  "text": "EzTaxon BLAST [CITATION_1] and ARB [CITATION_2] analyses showed that strain PP-F2F-G47 T shared 96.2 % 16S rRNA gene sequence similarity with M. daejeonensis Jip 10 T (AB267717), 95.7 % with Mucilaginibacter dorajii DR-f4 T (GU139697) and 95.5 % with M. phyllosphaerae PP-F2F-G21",
